  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t北京天安门广场边侧，中国革命历史博物馆<b>习近平革命历程馆</b>内容：<br/>\n<b>习近平革命起居馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平卧室全景<br/>\r\n—— 习近平被窝里面<br/>\r\n—— 习近平枕巾床单<br/>\r\n—— 习近平内裤内衣<br/>\r\n…<br/>\n<b>习近平革命气味馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平上身气味馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平中体气味馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平后部气味馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平下肢气味馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命印记馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平脚底印记馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平臀部印记馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平手掌印记馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命战斗馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平梁家河二百斤馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平福建形影动作馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平浙江指挥若定馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平北京登基称王馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平武汉病毒防疫馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命生活馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平幸梦雪馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平幸冰冰馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平幸丽媛馆…<br/>\r\n—— 习近平日常排泄馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平三餐内容馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平餐具碗筷馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平脱穿衣饰馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平走路爬坡馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命语言馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/video/6455\">通商宽衣</a>馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平遗屎弃纸馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平吃饱撑着馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命著作馆</b><br/>\r\n—— 习近平写作《<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41281\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/41281\">习近平全集</a>》馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平写作《习近平语录》馆<br/>\r\n—— 习近平写作《<a href=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3106\" title=\"https://www.pincong.rocks/article/3106\">康熙字典勘误</a>》馆<br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<b>习近平革命XYZ馆</b><br/>\r\n….<br/>\n<br/>\n<b><a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/article/38242\">乱世笑林</a></b><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9aam80d2laLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zjo4wiZ.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zjo4wiZ.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Zjo4wiZ.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9XYkQ4YXZ4LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/WbD8avx.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/WbD8avx.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/WbD8avx.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9Va3RKV2k0LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/UktJWi4.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/UktJWi4.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/UktJWi4.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9aUktrclN4LmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZRKkrSx.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZRKkrSx.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/ZRKkrSx.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9MUnZaeVNrLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/LRvZySk.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/LRvZySk.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LRvZySk.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS9sVnhGNzZqLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/lVxF76j.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/lVxF76j.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/lVxF76j.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9pLmltZ3VyLmNvbS93NHFidHRvLmpwZWc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://i.imgur.com/w4qbtto.jpeg\"><img alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/w4qbtto.jpeg\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/w4qbtto.jpeg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
